- THERE'S NO PLUS ONE HERE.
- I GET HOOKED UP,

10:16.616 --> 10:19.119
- YOU GET
HOOKED UP ALL THE TIME.
- YOU'VE NEVER GOTTEN A HOOKUP!

10:19.219 --> 10:20.821
