ANY SMALL THINGS.

10:24.992 --> 10:26.727
- IT'S THE SMALL THINGS, LARRY.
- ( doorbell rings )

10:26.827 --> 10:28.796
- THERE'S NO PLUS ONE.
- THERE'S ALWAYS A PLUS ONE.

10:29.997 --> 10:31.498
HI, IS THIS
LARRY DAVID'S HOUSE?

10:31.598 --> 10:35.502
- THIS IS LARRY DAVID.
