JOE'S DAUGHTER.

10:35.602 --> 10:37.304
- KYRA O'DONNELL!
- YEAH.

10:37.404 --> 10:38.939
- HEY.
- HEY.

10:39.039 --> 10:42.275
- UM, DO YOU LIKE
GIRL SCOUT COOKIES?
- I FIND THEM ABHORRENT.

10:42.375 --> 10:44.144
- BUT COME IN.
- OKAY, COOL.

10:44.244 --> 10:47.447
UM, SO WE'RE IN STOCK
ON A LOT OF THE COOKIES.

10:47.547 --> 10:48.949
- OKAY.
- WHICH IS GOOD NEWS.

10:49.049 --> 10:51.384
UM, WE HAVE THANK U
BERRY MUNCH COOKIES.

10:51.484 --> 10:53.553
OH, THANK U
BERRY MUNCH, OOOOH.

10:53.653 --> 10:55.723
TH-TH-TH-THANK U
BERRY MUNCH.

10:55.823 --> 10:58.391
( giggles )
WE HAVE THE TAGALONGS.

10:58.491 --> 10:59.592
- TAGALONGS.
- YEAH.

10:59.693 --> 11:01.628
WE HAVE THE...

11:01.729 --> 11:03.997
YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'M NOT EVEN INTERESTED.

11:04.097 --> 11:06.900
GIVE ME FIVE BOXES
OF EACH OF THEM.

11:07.000 --> 11:08.736
- REALLY?
- YEAH, WHAT DO YOU
SAY TO THAT?

11:08.836 --> 11:11.371
- THAT'S AWESOME.
- HUH? NOT BAD, RIGHT?

11:11.471 --> 11:14.074
OKAY, YEAH.
UM, WELL, YOU COULD JUST
TAKE A LOOK AT THAT.

11:14.174 --> 11:16.609
ALL RIGHT.
NOW YOU SEE, THESE SAMOAS,

11:16.710 --> 11:18.345
THAT LOOKS
PRETTY GOOD ACTUALLY.

11:18.445 --> 11:20.814
IT'S COVERED WITH CARAMEL,
ROLLED IN TOASTED COCONUT.

11:20.914 --> 11:23.683
'CAUSE I'M A HUGE
COCONUT GUY.

11:24.852 --> 11:26.887
EVERYTHING OKAY?

11:26.987 --> 11:32.359
I, UH, THINK I JUST HAD
MY FIRST PERIOD.

11:35.495 --> 11:38.799
OKAY.
THAT'S... YEAH.

11:38.899 --> 11:41.401
OKAY, SO THAT'S NO PROBLEM.

11:41.501 --> 11:43.636
THAT'S NO PROBLEM AT ALL.
YOU KNOW WHY?
IN FACT,

11:43.737 --> 11:46.273
I GOT AN EX-WIFE
AND I WAS MARRIED

11:46.373 --> 11:48.175
AND SHE'S A WOMAN.
SHE LEFT STUFF UPSTAIRS

11:48.275 --> 11:50.243
THAT'S GOING TO BE
VERY VALUABLE TO YOU.

11:50.343 --> 11:52.980
I'M GOING TO RUN UP
AND GET IT. YOU STAY
RIGHT HERE. DON'T MOVE.

11:53.080 --> 11:55.182
OKAY, DON'T WORRY.
YOU HAD IT IN THE RIGHT PLACE.

11:55.282 --> 11:58.018
I'M NOT KIDDING.
I GOT THIS.
I GOT THIS.

11:58.118 --> 12:00.487
STAY RIGHT THERE.
I'LL BE RIGHT DOWN.

12:00.587 --> 12:02.923
OK-KAY

12:03.791 --> 12:05.759
OKAY, GOT IT.

12:05.859 --> 12:09.362
HERE YOU GO,
ALL RIGHT.

12:12.299 --> 12:13.733
ALL RIGHT, GOOD LUCK.

