UM, I DON'T REALLY KNOW
HOW TO USE ONE OF THESE.

12:18.872 --> 12:21.942
OH, OKAY, ALL RIGHT.
THERE'S INSTRUCTIONS HERE.

12:23.777 --> 12:26.013
UM...

12:27.848 --> 12:29.983
OKAY OKAY.

12:30.083 --> 12:32.219
"IF YOU'RE USING A TAMPON,
YOU'LL SEE THAT

12:32.319 --> 12:34.487
THE PLASTIC APPLICATOR
