"PLASTIC APPLICATOR"?

12:37.290 --> 12:39.292
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT THIS IS.

12:41.328 --> 12:43.363
I JUST DON'T GET
WHAT YOU'RE SAYING.

12:44.631 --> 12:46.499
OH OKAY.

12:46.599 --> 12:49.336
"HOLD THE APPLICATOR LIGHTLY
ON THE OUTER INSERTION TUBE

12:49.436 --> 12:51.704
AT THE GRIP LOCATION WITH YOUR
THUMB AND MIDDLE FINGER."

12:51.805 --> 12:53.373
- WHAT THE FUCK?
- LIGHTLY?

12:53.473 --> 12:55.375
- WHAT DO--
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED TO--
- WAIT A SECOND.

12:55.475 --> 12:57.845
"GENTLY SLIDE THE APPLICATOR
ALL THE WAY INTO YOUR VAGI--"

12:57.945 --> 13:00.547
HOW DO I KNOW
IF I'M DOING IT RIGHT?

13:00.647 --> 13:04.384
