20:45.244 --> 20:47.046
- BECAUSE OF BERG!
- YES, BECAUSE OF BERG.

20:47.146 --> 20:48.515
- BECAUSE OF BERG.
- YES.

20:48.615 --> 20:51.518
- I'VE OFTEN WONDERED
WOULD PEOPLE...
- REALLY?

20:51.618 --> 20:53.753
- ...THINK THAT.
