ABOUT THE LONDON TRIP...

22:27.179 --> 22:29.449
- YEAH?
- ...I STARTED TO REALIZE,
"WAIT A MINUTE.

22:29.549 --> 22:32.284
IF I DID GO TO EUROPE
WITHOUT HER, I'D COME BACK

22:32.385 --> 22:35.422
AND IT WOULD BE 20 MORE
YEARS OF BOREDOM."

22:35.522 --> 22:38.758
