"LOOK, LET'S GET A DIVORCE."

22:38.858 --> 22:40.059
SHE SAID OKAY.

22:40.159 --> 22:43.229
I'M GONNA BE SINGLE!

22:43.329 --> 22:45.064
- YOU AND ME!
- WOW.

22:45.164 --> 22:46.466
- IS THAT GREAT?
- MY MAN.

22:46.566 --> 22:48.034
CONGRATULATIONS.
CONGRATULATIONS.

22:48.134 --> 22:50.403
