WHEN YOU GET A FUCKING
DIVORCE?

22:50.503 --> 22:53.239
RIDE AROUND AND BUMP THE HORN
AND SHIT LIKE MOTHERFUCKERS
GETTING MARRIED.

22:53.339 --> 22:55.274
- WHAT A GREAT IDEA.
- GOD DAMN RIGHT.

22:55.374 --> 22:57.544
- PUT CANS ON YOUR CAR,
BEEP YOUR HORN.
- "JUST DIVORCED."

22:57.644 --> 22:59.912
- Larry: "JUST DIVORCED."
- I'M EXCITED I'M SINGLE.

23:00.012 --> 23:02.014
GET OUT THERE
AND GET SOME NEW ASS,
KNOW WHAT I'M SAYING?

23:02.114 --> 23:04.350
YOU DONE RAN THAT OTHER ASS
IN THE GROUND, RIGHT?

23:04.451 --> 23:06.018
UH, I DON'T WANT TO TALK
ABOUT MY WIFE LIKE THAT.

23:06.118 --> 23:08.020
YOU RAN THAT ASS IN THE GROUND
AND YOU'RE MOVING ON, RIGHT?

23:08.120 --> 23:10.089
I DIDN'T RUN ANY--
WE HAD A NICE MARRIAGE
FOR 20 YEARS.

23:10.189 --> 23:13.025
- NO, YOU RAN
THAT ASS IN THE GROUND.
- I DON'T RUN PEOPLE'S ASS

23:13.125 --> 23:14.727
- IN THE GROUND.
- ALL MEN DO.

23:14.827 --> 23:17.664
IT'S NOT A NEGATIVE THING
TO RUN AN ASS IN THE GROUND.
THAT'S ALL.

23:17.764 --> 23:19.766
Leon:
YOU RAN THAT SHIT IN THE GROUD
LIKE A RENT-A-CAR.

23:19.866 --> 23:21.868
- WHAT'S WITH YOU?
- WHAT DO YOU MEAN
WHAT'S WITH ME?

23:21.968 --> 23:24.671
- WHAT ARE YOU SO GLUM ABOUT?
- IT'S JUST THAT EVERYBODY'S

23:24.771 --> 23:26.873
GETTING A CHANCE TO GET
DIVORCED EXCEPT ME.

23:26.973 --> 23:29.275
YOU GET DIVORCED,
YOU GET DIVORCED,

23:29.375 --> 23:30.877
YOU DON'T EVEN NEED
TO GET DIVORCED.

23:30.977 --> 23:33.379
EVEN THE OWNER OF THE DODGERS,
O'DONNELL, HE GETS A DIVORCE.

23:33.480 --> 23:35.214
Larry:
SHIT, I JUST
REALIZED SOMETHING.

23:35.314 --> 23:38.751
O'DONNELL'S GOT THE SWEDE.
I SHOULD REALLY TELL HIM
ABOUT BERG.

23:38.851 --> 23:41.087
- WHAT'S WRONG WITH BERG?
- HE'S NOT A JEW.

23:41.187 --> 23:43.122
- HE'S A SWEDE.
- HE IS?

23:43.222 --> 23:45.492
I WAS AT HIS HOUSE
FOR HANUKAH.

23:47.326 --> 23:49.596
- HE'S A SWEDE?
- A SWEDE.

23:49.696 --> 23:52.131
- YOU'RE KIDDING ME?
- NO, HE'S A SWEDE.

23:52.231 --> 23:53.933
I JUST--
I MEAN--

23:54.033 --> 23:56.603
I KNEW THERE WAS SOMETHING
THAT DIDN'T ADD UP
ABOUT THAT GUY.

23:56.703 --> 23:58.805
- IT'S TRUE.
- HE TOOK ME FOR A RIDE,
THAT'S WHAT HE DID.

23:58.905 --> 24:01.173
- UNBELIEVABLE.
- I DO APPRECIATE YOU

24:01.273 --> 24:02.709
