TO TELL ME THIS.

24:02.809 --> 24:04.611
I MEAN, YOU DIDN'T
HAVE TO AT ALL.

24:04.711 --> 24:06.813
ESPECIALLY CONSIDERING WHAT
HAPPENED WITH MY DAUGHTER.

24:06.913 --> 24:09.348
- I FELT I HAD TO TELL YOU.
- I DON'T KNOW WHAT
I'M GONNA DO NOW.

24:09.448 --> 24:12.018
I MEAN, I AM FIGHTING
FOR EVERYTHING HERE.

24:12.118 --> 24:14.987
I COULD LOSE THIS
ENTIRE ORGANIZATION.
THIS WHOLE TEAM!

24:15.087 --> 24:17.824
- I GOT A LOT AT STAKE MYSELF.
- ( sighs )

24:20.627 --> 24:22.929
YOU KNOW WHAT?

24:23.029 --> 24:24.864
