24:26.566 --> 24:29.536
- YOU SURE YOU'RE REALLY JEWISH?
- I'M THE REAL DEAL.

24:36.843 --> 24:38.277
- HOW FUN IS THIS?
- HOW GREAT IS THIS?

24:38.377 --> 24:39.746
TWO SINGLE GUYS
AT A BALLGAME

24:39.846 --> 24:41.280
AND WE'RE SITTING
IN THE OWNER'S BOX.

24:41.380 --> 24:42.782
I KNOW.
HOW ABOUT THAT?

24:42.882 --> 24:44.951
CAN YOU BELIEVE THAT STUPID
REMARK YOU SAID TO ME

24:45.051 --> 24:47.554
- CHANGED MY LIFE
FOR THE BETTER.
- ISN'T IT INCREDIBLE?

24:47.654 --> 24:49.255
OH, I LOVE YOU!
HOW IS THAT LAWYER?

24:49.355 --> 24:51.257
- HIRIAM KATZ, HE'S FANTASTIC.
- HE MUST BE GREAT.

24:51.357 --> 24:54.360
HE REDID MY ENTIRE
DIVORCE SETTLEMENT.
YOU'VE GOT TO USE HIM.

24:54.460 --> 24:55.862
- I WILL USE HIM.
- NAMES PLEASE.

24:55.962 --> 24:59.699
LARRY DAVID,
MARTY FUNKHOUSER.

24:59.799 --> 25:01.834
I'M SORRY, GENTLEMEN.
YOUR NAMES ARE NOT
ON THE LIST.

25:01.934 --> 25:04.537
NO NO NO.

25:04.637 --> 25:06.773
LARRY DAVID. I'M A FRIEND
OF JOE O'DONNELL'S.

25:06.873 --> 25:09.308
OH, MR. O'DONNELL
NO LONGER OWNS THE TEAM.

25:09.408 --> 25:11.644
- WHAT?
