HAVE AN ASSISTANT.

25:46.178 --> 25:48.147
- ( beeps )
- KATZ, IT'S LARRY.

25:48.247 --> 25:50.650
DON'T SIGN ANYTHING.
I'M ON MY WAY UP TO YOUR OFFICE.

25:59.759 --> 26:02.461
ASSHOLE!
YOU COST ME THE DODGERS.

26:02.561 --> 26:03.996
( groans )

26:06.098 --> 26:07.834
( moaning )

26:07.934 --> 26:09.969
HE HIT ME.

26:14.540 --> 26:17.610
DON'T WORRY.
I THINK I'VE GOT SOMETHING
THAT WILL STOP THE BLEEDING.

26:17.710 --> 26:19.511
- I THINK IT'S WORKING.
- IT'S DOING THE JOB.

26:19.612 --> 26:21.814
- THANK YOU SO MUCH.
- I THINK YOU'RE
GONNA BE FINE.

26:21.914 --> 26:24.250
