- TAKE CARE.

26:24.350 --> 26:27.419
WHAT IS IN YOUR NOSE?

26:27.519 --> 26:29.288
IT'S A TAMPON.

26:31.057 --> 26:33.826
WELL, I GOT HIT IN THE FACE.
WHAT WAS I SUPPOSED TO DO?

26:33.926 --> 26:36.528
- IT STOPPED THE BLEEDING.
- OKAY.

26:36.629 --> 26:39.632
UM, SO YOU KNOW, I JUST
SIGNED THE PAPERS.

26:39.732 --> 26:41.500
AND I GOT THE HOUSE

26:41.600 --> 26:44.503
SO YOU HAVE 24 HOURS
TO VACATE THE PREMISES.

26:44.603 --> 26:46.639
