AND BRING YOUR STUFF DOWN.

27:48.100 --> 27:50.402
- FUCK YOU, LARRY.
- FUCK YOU, LEON.

27:50.502 --> 27:52.271
( doorbell rings )

27:53.605 --> 27:55.007
HI, MR. LARRY DAVID,

27:55.107 --> 27:57.009
